2026-03-28T10:35:27.755Z JOY-0080 comment.added "Implements ADR-021. Guard is the Guardianship pillar of AI Governance. All write operations pass through joy_core::guard for validation against the project's Trust Model. Progressive activation: passthrough for solo, full enforcement for enterprise." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
